*rŏk'i, /ˈrɒki/, /<tt>"rQki</tt>/
*:Rhymes: <span class="IPA" style="font-family:{{IPA fonts}};">[[Rhymes:English:-ɒki|-ɒki]]</span>
*Audio files
*:Received Pronunciation: <span class="IPA" style="font-family:{{IPA fonts}};">[ˈɹʷɒkiː]</span>
